Description:
Read symbolic links into a buffer without size limitation, relative to fd.

Files:
lib/careadlinkat.c
lib/careadlinkat.h

Depends-on:
allocator
idx
minmax
ssize_t
unistd

configure.ac:
AC_REQUIRE([AC_C_RESTRICT])
AC_CHECK_FUNCS_ONCE([readlinkat])

Makefile.am:
lib_SOURCES += careadlinkat.c

Include:
"careadlinkat.h"

